{"tid":1607000,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"隊友們，出黎湊下人數都唔肯？","createTime":"2019-09-30T16:59:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T17:56:33.000Z","uid":51171,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2ad084a2e4c75818363c78889899745190848379","tid":1607000,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:59:13.000Z","msg":"而家唔係要你出黎一定踢前鋒、狂轟對面幾多球，你驚俾對面剷傷，OK，<br />\n咁企最後打龍行行企企得喇呱？<br />\n笠件波衫坐後備席、壯下隊波嘅氣勢得喇呱？<br />\n<br />\n場波要齊人先可以開始比賽，唔夠人係直接判輸。<br />\n你踢咩位都無所謂，做觀眾都好，但如果連家門都唔肯踏出嘅話，老實講，有啲過份。丢低其餘十個著齊波衫係場上面嘅隊友，哩喺屋企睇live，睇住啲隊友一開波直接被判出局，坦白講句：唔好咁自私，勇敢一次。<br />\n<br />\n其實人地都驚、人地都有包袱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、人地都有父母生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、人地都會痛，而而家只不過叫你出黎湊下人數，你都唔肯嗎？<br />\n<br />\n你驚，正常，任何人都驚，驚 其實就正正代表我地嘅自由同權利已經(already)被對手剝奪左，<br />\n點解我地應有嘅自由同權利要被剝奪！<br />\n邊個搞到我驚！<br />\n點解我要驚你啊！<br />\n<br />\n你驚，但你冷靜落黎，你唔會因此而嬲咩？  笠件波衫落黎鳩叫扮識踢波啦手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：<br />\n左翼，有做開善事，<br />\n但唔識入波(睇我名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)。"},{"pid":"01ed0cac76d1abeb2fbb738d32e63b3c1b6b7e76","tid":1607000,"uid":127454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:33:08.000Z","msg":"出嚟現場睇波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c3b3b8674a2f8ae36f0fa44e9056d189dc059c3","tid":1607000,"uid":4496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:35:17.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n<br />\n仲有見到隊友求救<br />\n有人嗑跟隊打波<br />\n一定要幫手嗑幫手跟隊"},{"pid":"b80bb4a7be4f099b65f89b229c85623e9b2d360e","tid":1607000,"uid":71657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:36:38.000Z","msg":"跟隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24fe92617ca73f041c5be7d676975de8ae7291b3","tid":1607000,"uid":53034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:36:49.000Z","msg":"聽日唔出仲衰過藍絲"},{"pid":"da3b1182d0badee6951f41fe33a41c91043dbf67","tid":1607000,"uid":94915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:37:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DDsyo51.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDDsyo51.png&h=d69489e0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">周圍派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />周圍貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />周圍畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用自己方法，唔好諗住齋行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己帶野出去</span></span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n6月頭，呢場運動流第一滴血𠴱陣已經有用黑洋紫荊旗，手足仲升埋旗，但好似未有人正式講過<br />\n我而家就宣佈，呢支黑洋紫荊旗係我地嘅 <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n港。殤。旗 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Remembrance Flag</span></span></strong></span>！！<br />\n紀念嘅係我地不論勇和喺戰場喺狗屋流過嘅每一滴血，失去過嘅每一位手足，紀念香港人抗爭嘅每一年每一日！<br />\n￼<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JaHqWAY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJaHqWAY.jpg&h=c4deb4cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但記唔記得點解可以有嗰<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">5粒星</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！！！！！我地一路反共反支一路又用番污染咗嘅洋紫荊make唔make sense啊！！？？？？粒星代表<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">共產黨啊屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n要用就用純白花！港殤啊！去共啊！！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fZpkLtE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfZpkLtE.jpg&h=0d7f08e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n￼全部人同我print定堆張離出黎 10月1 fing 爆佢連儂牆貼爆佢啊！<br />\n當榮光歸香港，我地會有一支真正屬於我地嘅旗，唔L係共紅色嗰支啊。到時後呢一支 Rememberance Flag 就係用離紀念我地嘅勝利，嗰日離之前我地就高舉我地嘅黑旗克L死共匪！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/72RLfcH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F72RLfcH.jpg&h=b3fd5d7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kcCeSZn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkcCeSZn.jpg&h=3322addc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wVhKvL3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwVhKvL3.jpg&h=60f790fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kECB6jp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkECB6jp.jpg&h=ffd08f5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NMymxZp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNMymxZp.jpg&h=a92c1832&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xrOarjq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxrOarjq.jpg&h=de867e8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fWzACq6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfWzACq6.jpg&h=5d14df1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">唔好諗住齋行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己帶野出去</span></span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">周圍派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />周圍貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />周圍畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">唔好諗住齋行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己帶野出去</span></span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">周圍派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />周圍貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />周圍畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">唔好諗住齋行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己帶野出去</span></span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">周圍派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />周圍貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />周圍畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">唔好諗住齋行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己帶野出去</span></span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">周圍派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />周圍貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />周圍畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"4f6fcff01c92505ef9672bb0cc22f5cfc12e43da","tid":1607000,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01ed0cac76d1abeb2fbb738d32e63b3c1b6b7e76","tid":1607000,"uid":127454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:33:08.000Z","msg":"出嚟現場睇波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:38:18.000Z","msg":"你聽日打右閘定中場"},{"pid":"6ed3d53f060d08a7afa2e2d68bf62eb86478c7c2","tid":1607000,"uid":261478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:39:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0380d262e5ddab253283a4d295424efa839fd7f","tid":1607000,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24fe92617ca73f041c5be7d676975de8ae7291b3","tid":1607000,"uid":53034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:36:49.000Z","msg":"聽日唔出仲衰過藍絲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:45:15.000Z","msg":"又未至於，係有啲自私囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你條命就寶貴啲，<br />\n前線條命就低賤啲....<br />\n你擁有嘅就唔可以失去，<br />\n人地擁有嘅就可以由佢失去.....<br />\n<br />\n咁嘅feel囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a45af5c662d222187decdbdcfc5aff5c51a032f","tid":1607000,"uid":107611,"like":